<Base
  title="How Many Brands Should You Pitch to Land One Sponsorship?"
  description="Cold sponsorship pitches follow cold email math: with targeted lists and a 3–4 touch sequence, expect one closed deal per 30–80 well-chosen brands. The funnel stage by stage, and what moves each conversion."
